ional assisting party who helps with the exchange of quantum\ninformation, and we establish semi-definite programming lower bounds on the\nsimulation error for this task. More generally, we provide semi-definite\nprogramming lower bounds on the performance of bipartite and multipartite\nchannel simulation using a shared resource state and LOCC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2020 17:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 9 Apr 2022 17:02:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2022 20:25:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-21"}
