inting towards increasing\nurban sprawl and stagnant growth in urban centres across cities of all sizes.\nIt also has theoretical implications on the nature of sprawl and its scaling\nwith city size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2020 14:01:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-19"}
