ant for prediction. We demonstrate the technique by explaining neural\nnetworks fit to explosion optical spectral-temporal signatures for predicting\ncharacteristics of the explosive devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2020 22:33:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-26"}
